        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-4" itemprop="headline">
          Cara Deploy Fullstack App React + Go Fiber ke AWS EC2 dengan Docker &amp; GitHub Actions CI/CD
