        <p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed" itemprop="description">
          Panduan lengkap dari nol: setup EC2, Docker Compose, Nginx reverse proxy, SSL,
          sampai CI/CD pipeline otomatis yang berjalan tiap push ke main branch.
          Semua berdasarkan pengalaman langsung deploy proyek
          <a href="https://school.lananuranf.my.id/" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline">Letta School</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm font-bold">L</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
              <span itemprop="name">Maulana Nur Anfajm</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal"> (Lananuranf)</span>
            </p>
